        <script>
        $('#air_travel,#public_transport,#private_transport,#domestic_lockdown,#schools,#restaurants,#events,#gatherings').click(function() {
            var href = $(this).find('a').attr('href');
            if(href!='#') window.open(href, '_blank');
        });
        $('.restriction_link').click(function(e) {
            e.preventDefault();
            //if($(this).attr('href')!='#') return false;
            //else return true;
        });
        var cities = [];
        var graph_type = 'line';
        var city = '';   
        $('#myTab2 a').on('click', function (e) {
            graph_type = $(this).text().trim()=='Linear' ? 'line' : 'logarithmic';
            $('#myTab a.active').click();
        });
        $('#myTab a').on('click', function (e) {
            title = $(this).text();
            var date = new Date();
            var timestamp = date.getTime();
            $.getJSON("history.json?_="+timestamp, function(response, status) {
                if(status=='success') {
                    if(response) {
                        categories='';data_cases = '';data_active = '';data_recoveries = '';data_deaths = '';cases = '0';active = '0';recoveries = '0';deaths = '0';
                        var output = Object.entries(response).map(([key, value]) => ({key,value}));
                        output.forEach(function(object, index) {
                            date = object['key'];
                            data = object['value'];
                            d = new Date(date);
                            mo = new Intl.DateTimeFormat('en', { month: '2-digit' }).format(d);
                            da = new Intl.DateTimeFormat('en', { day: '2-digit' }).format(d);
                            if(title.toLowerCase()=='world') {
                                categories += '"'+da+'.'+mo+'",';
                                data_cases += data['total_cases']+',';
                                data_active += data['total_active']+',';
                                data_deaths += data['total_deaths']+',';
                                data_recoveries += data['total_recoveries']+',';
                                cases = data['total_cases'];active = data['total_active'];deaths = data['total_deaths'];recoveries = data['total_recoveries'];
                            } else {
                                if(title.toLowerCase()=='united states') title = 'USA';
                                if(title.toLowerCase()=='south korea') title = 'S. Korea';
                                if(title.toLowerCase()=='united kingdom') title = 'UK';
                                if(title.toLowerCase()=='united arab emirates') title = 'UAE';
                                if(data['countries'] !== undefined) {
                                    var output2 = Object.entries(data['countries']).map(([key, value]) => ({key,value}));
                                    output2.forEach(function(object2, index) {
                                        country = object2['key'];
                                        data2 = object2['value'];
                                        if(title.toLowerCase()==country.toLowerCase()) {
                                            categories += '"'+da+'.'+mo+'",';
                                            data_cases += data2['cases']+',';
                                            data_active += data2['active']+',';
                                            data_deaths += data2['deaths']+',';
                                            data_recoveries += data2['recoveries']+',';
                                            cases = data2['cases'];active = data2['active'];deaths = data2['deaths'];recoveries = data2['recoveries'];
                                            // break;
                                        }
                                    });
                                }
                            }
                        });
                        categories = '['+categories.replace(/,$/,'')+']';
                        graph = '[{"name":"Confirmed Cases", "color": "#FB7E24", "lineWidth": 2, "data": ['+data_cases.replace(/,$/,'')+']},{"name":"Deceased ", "color": "#848484", "lineWidth": 2, "data": ['+data_deaths.replace(/,$/,'')+']}]';
                        $('span#cases').text(cases);
                        $('span#deaths').text(deaths);
                        graph = JSON.parse(graph);
                        categories = JSON.parse(categories);
                        Highcharts.chart('myChart', { chart: { type: 'line' }, title: { text: title }, subtitle: { text: '' }, xAxis: { categories: categories }, yAxis: { title: { text: '' }, type: graph_type }, legend: { layout: 'vertical', align: 'right', verticalAlign: 'middle' }, credits: { enabled: false }, series: graph, responsive: { rules: [{ condition: { maxWidth: 800 }, chartOptions: { legend: { layout: 'horizontal', align: 'center', verticalAlign: 'bottom' } } }] } });
                        
                    }
                }
            });
            if(city) {
                $('#links_section').addClass('d-none');
                $('#hashtags_section').addClass('d-none');
                $('#links_section p').html('');
                $('#hashtags_section p').html('');
                $('#air_travel span.small-headline').html('Air Travel');
                $('#air_travel').css('background-color', '#FFF');
                $('#air_travel a').attr('href', '#');
                $('#public_transport span.small-headline').html('Public Transport');
                $('#public_transport').css('background-color', '#FFF');
                $('#public_transport a').attr('href', '#');
                $('#private_transport span.small-headline').html('Private Transport');
                $('#private_transport').css('background-color', '#FFF');
                $('#private_transport a').attr('href', '#');
                $('#domestic_lockdown span.small-headline').html('Domestic Lockdown');
                $('#domestic_lockdown').css('background-color', '#FFF');
                $('#domestic_lockdown a').attr('href', '#');
                $('#schools span.small-headline').html('Schools');
                $('#schools').css('background-color', '#FFF');
                $('#schools a').attr('href', '#');
                $('#restaurants span.small-headline').html('Restaurants');
                $('#restaurants').css('background-color', '#FFF');
                $('#restaurants a').attr('href', '#');
                $('#events span.small-headline').html('Events');
                $('#events').css('background-color', '#FFF');
                $('#events a').attr('href', '#');
                $('#gatherings span.small-headline').html('Gatherings');
                $('#gatherings').css('background-color', '#FFF');
                $('#gatherings a').attr('href', '#');
                country_code = '';
                cities.forEach(function(item, index) {
                    if((item[0].toLowerCase()==city.toLowerCase()) || (item[1].toLowerCase()==title.toLowerCase())) {
                        country_code = item[2];
                    }
                });
                $.get("restrictions.csv", function(response, status) {
                    if(status=='success') {
                        if(response) {

        <script>
            var date = new Date();
            var timestamp = date.getTime();
            var cities = [];
            $.getJSON("cities.json", function(response, status){
                if(status=='success') {
                    if(response) {
                        search_terms = [];
                        response.forEach(function(item, index) {
                            search_terms.push(item['name']+', '+item['country']);
                            cities.push([item['name'],item['country'],item['code']]);
                        });
                        $('#form-autocomplete').haffAutocomplete({
                            data: search_terms
                        });
                    }
                }
            });
            $("body").on("change", "#form-autocomplete", function() {
                city = '';
                setTimeout(function(){
                    var title = $("#form-autocomplete").val();
                    county_part = title.split(',');
                    if(county_part.length>0) {
                        city = county_part[0].trim();
                        title = county_part[1].trim();
                        $("a#city-tab").text(title);
                        $("a#city-tab").click();
                    } else {
                        setTimeout(function(){
                            var title = $("#form-autocomplete").val();
                            county_part = title.split(',');
                            if(county_part.length>0) {
                                city = county_part[0].trim();
                                title = county_part[1].trim();
                                $("a#city-tab").text(title);
                                $("a#city-tab").click();
                            }
                        },200);
                    }
                },200);
            });
        </script>
        <script>
            $("#share").jsSocials({
                shareIn: "popup",
                showCount: true,
                showLabel: true,
                shares: ["twitter", "facebook", "linkedin", "pinterest"/* , "messenger" */]
            });

        </script>
